*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZPRG_SAMPLE_SUB
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZPRG_SAMPLE_SUB.

DATA : lv_out TYPE numc3.

PARAMETERS : lv_in1 TYPE numc3.
PARAMETERS : lv_in2 TYPE numc3.

PERFORM sum.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form sum
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM sum .
 lv_out = lv_in1 + lv_in2.
 MESSAGE lv_out TYPE 'I'.
ENDFORM.
